# AI / LLM (when the system integrates AI)

- **RAG**: fetch relevant context before sending to the model
- **AI cost control**: never send full tables/datasets without need
- **Context compression** for long context
- **Prompt versioning** as code (versioned, reviewable)
- **Human in the loop** for critical or irreversible actions
